<br>
<br>
Pets are always same level now, so always same hp.<br>
<br>
I did the tests WITHOUT any kind of foci myself and no specializations in heals.<br>
<br>
I sicked pet on mob and jammed the report health key, taking several samples on each fight.<br>
<br>
Did the math<br>
<br>
Example:<br>
<br>
I have 95 percent health<br>
Mob its Jobober for 10 damage<br>
I have 90 percent health.<br>
<br>
5 percent = 10 hp<br>
X               X<br>
20              20<br>
------------------<br>
100%     =   200HP<br>
<br>
<br>
And then did another test same way with foci on pet:<br>
<br>
2 ears, 2 rings, 2 wrists, a Mantle and a Neck: Used middle ring of foci.  So added...  <br>
80 hp...<br>
<br>
<br>
And redid the test above...<br>
<br>
Came out with exactly 80 more HP on pet EVERY time...<br>
<br>
Cara<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
PS: No idea on if the actual EFFECTS work<br>
